name: The Frequency supporting SIRPICO EP Launch @ The Winchester
description:
The Frequency will be supporting fellow local band SIRPICO at their EP Launch at The Winchester, Bournemouth on Saturday 6th April 2013.
We have a limited number of advance tickets of £2.50 ea.
When there gone there gone!

name: "Fall To The Floor" - New Debut Album
description:
The brand new debut album "Fall To The Floor" from The Frequency.
9 Rocking tracks to satisfy your rock n roll needs!

Track-listing

1.New York Symphony
2.Steal A Phrase
3.Same Old Nothing At All
4.Sticky Little Finger
5.You Don’t Have To Know
6.Sympathy For Insanity
7.Save Today
8.Loverblind
9.I Know,You Know

Band Members: Austyn Brown-Vox/Guitars
Dan Kazimirow-Guitars/Vox
Dan Hammond-Smith-Bass/Vox
Phil Hodgetts-Drums/Vocals

http://www.thefrequencyuk.com
http://www.twitter.com/thefrequencyuk
